flowchart TD

A[Prepare Room Booking Prototype]
--> B[Select Student and Staff Test Users]

B --> C[Explain Experiment Objective]

C --> D[Student Uses Student Portal]

D --> E[View Available Rooms]

E --> F[Search for a Room]

F --> G[Book a Room]

G --> H[View My Bookings]

H --> I[Cancel Booking]

I --> J[Staff Uses Admin Portal]

J --> K[Manage Rooms]

K --> L[View Dashboard]

L --> M[Collect User Feedback]

M --> N[Evaluate Results]

N --> O{Did Users Complete Tasks Successfully?}

O -->|Yes| P[Proceed with Final Prototype]

O -->|No| Q[Improve Prototype and Repeat Testing]
